					<h1 class="art_h1 lineheight30px">LEONESSAbrevini obtained the ISO9001:2008 Quality Management System Certification</h1>
					<div class="info">2013-07-31 Click：[13]</div>
					<div class="mh464 lineheight30px">
					&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style='font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;'>In May 2013, LEONESSAbrevini (Yancheng) Slewing Bearings Co., Ltd has got the long-awaited ISO 9001:2008 certification after 3 days strictly audit by DNV (DNV CERTIFICATION B.V., THE NETHERLANDS). The certificate is valid for the following product or service ranges: MANUFACTURE OF BALL AND ROLLER SLEWING BEARINGS.</span><span style='font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;'>&nbsp;</span>
<p class='MsoNormal'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;
mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN'>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; To ensure to get through the audit successfully, LEONESSAbrevini held on an ISO Quality training class in January and founded a certification leading group, in which all the department managers acted as the core. After compiling the quality system documents, LEONESSAbrevini conducted a three-month trial period, two times internal audit, one time management review and simulation test based on these documents. At the end of May, 2013, after the strictly audit in LEONESSAbrevini, the audit team agreed that the Quality Policy and Quality Target are scientific and matching the enterprise actual situation; the quality system documents meet the standard of ISO 9001:2008.</span><span style='font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;'>&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class='MsoNormal'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;
mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN'>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;As always, LEONESSAbrevini uphold the quality policy which are&rdquo; Quality utmost, customer oriented, all-staff participation and continuous improvement&rdquo; to continuously improve the efficiency, the management level and product competitiveness. All those effort lays a solid foundation for high quality products and excellent after-sale service.</span><span style='font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;'>&nbsp;<br />
<br />
</span><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;
mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN'>(Attachment: Certification picture)<br />
</span></p>
